display_long_description:
Welcome to GELADA!
A Game containing an absolute TON of ideas, including some we accept FROM THE COMMUNITY.

Drop some down in our DISCORD: https://discord.gg/EFqx763jvN
Check out our privacy policy for any concerns, if any concerns pop up, please send over a message to my email: darkifiedd@gmail.com

I've spent approximately 4-6 months alone learning how to use unity, on a previous game that I had named "Ape City".
Of course at that time I knew pretty much nothing about unity, but I learned.

With the help of Malex (developer of Just Chimpin + more) + Spacer (beta tester, developer supporting future pc exploits being shut down) we managed to develop the game you currently know as "Gelada".

Thank you all, seriously, it means a lot.

Also P.S. 
Watch out for "him"...
